The Nuby Coolbite Fruit Teethers have been designed with multiple textures to give your infant an array of surfaces to chew on.

The Farlin Effort Saving Manual Breast Pump has been designed to help new mothers express and store breast milk in a safe
column17: hygienic and comfortable manner. The ergonomic manual breast pump can easily be used with one hand and simulates your baby\'s suckling action to naturally encourage let-down and allow you to express breast milk with ease. The soft silicone liner in the breastshield offers comfort and gently massages the breast to promote the milk flow. The practical adjustable dial enables pressure control
column18: offering maximum comfort. The manual breast pump is easy to assemble and has a compact design allowing you to discreetly use the pump at home or even when you travel. The easy-to-use breast pump comes with a 150 cc polypropylene storage container with a cover and can be converted into a nursing bottle with the silicone teat. column19: you no longer have to depend on loud motors
column21:

\r\n

column22: however boiling is not recommended as it may affect the elasticity and the suction effect of the pump. The breast milk storage bottle
column25:

The shield of the pacifier has ventilation holes to allow the circulation of air and also has a swivel ring that allows you to take the pacifier out of your baby\u2019s mouth with ease. The Flip It Non Drip Straw Mega Sipper from Nuby has been designed with soft silicone spouts that are soft for an infant's mouth. These BPA free Nuby Sippers will help active toddlers to drink from the straw. The silicone straw lets the tiny tots to drink naturally from the Nuby Mega Sipper without any fuss and difficulty. An easy flip top cap that covers the soft spout keeps the sipper covered and safe from contamination.

The no-spill feature of these Nuby Sippers make them perfect travelling partners. The flip cap will keep the sipper clean and hygienic. As your bundle of joy grows old enough to drink directly from the cup then you can easily flip back the top of the sipper and use this as a normal cup. Fluids move across the straw only when it is sipped

'desc': [u'

Nuby Coolbite Fruit Teether (Orange) Price: Rs.175

Teethers are provided to infants who begin to develop their milk teeth. During this phase babies will feel pain and irritation on their gums owing to the emerging teeth. To relieve the pain and irritations the tiny tot will resort to biting that will put pressure on the gums which will soothe the ache to some extent. At such instances providing your bundle of joy with a good teether will prevent them from biting into anything and everything. The Nuby Coolbite Fruit Teethers have been designed with multiple textures to give your infant an array of surfaces to chew on.

The patented purIce gel that is integrated into the Nuby Coolbite Teether will help in retaining a cold temperature for a longer time after refrigerating. The cool temperature will help in relieving the ache in a much better way than a normal teether. These Nuby Teethers are designed and sized in such a way that they fit effortlessly into the baby’s tiny hands and allows them to hold the teether with a firm grip. You can use these Nuby Coolbite Teethers for your infants once they are three months old or above.

Farlin Orthodontic - Glow in Dark Price: Rs.175

Every new parent has been jolted out of bed in the middle of the night by the cries of their baby. As you get to your baby’s room
column13: half asleep and jostled by your baby\u2019s sharp crying
column14:
you find it almost impossible to locate your little one\u2019s pacifier. Farlin understands how parents can find these midnight tussles absolutely stressful and has created a very practical pacifier that can make life so much simpler. The Farlin Orthodontic - Glow in the Dark pacifier glows in the dark and allows you to find the pacifier in the jiffy and calm your baby in no time. The pacifier renders orthodontic advantages as well.

\r\n

\r\n\tMade from high quality silicone this firm and flexible pacifier promotes the natural development of your baby\u2019s palate
column15:
teeth and gums. The pacifier is soft and easy to suck and reduces pressure on the jaw during sucking. The bulb of the teat is designed to allow proper tongue placement during sucking. The glow-in-the-dark pacifier from Farlin is suitable for babies aged 6 to 8 months. The pacifier is durable and maintains its shape even after long use. The shield of the pacifier has ventilation holes to allow the circulation of air and also has a swivel ring that allows you to take the pacifier out of your baby\u2019s mouth with ease. Now you can enjoy peace and quiet while you put your baby to bed or prepare their bottle and your baby enjoys soothing comfort with the Farlin Orthodontic pacifier.

\n

'desc': [u'

Nuby Microwave Sterilizer - 4 Slots (White) Price: Rs.800

Sterilization is a process that no parent can overlook. Baby bottles have to be sterilized properly to ensure that they are germ-free and that your baby is safe from illness. But the process of sterilization can be tedious
column13: especially if you intend to do it over the stove. The Nuby Microwave Sterilizer gives you a quick and hassle-free way to sterilize baby bottles. This microwave sterilizer has a compact design and offers an easy and hygienic way to sterilize your little one\u2019s bottles. Holding 4 bottles at once
column14: the sterilizer uses the principles of steam heat to kill germs and sterilize the bottles
column15:
keeping them sterile for up to 3 hours.

\r\n

\r\n\tTo use the steam sterilizer
column16: fill the centre reservoir with tap water up to 200 ml. Before placing the sterilizer in the microwave
column17: turn the vent to the open position to release excess steam. The sterilizer takes 8 minutes to sterilize when the microwave is set to full power on 475 to 850 W and just 5 minutes to sterilize when set to full power on 850W to 1100 W. The sterilizer must be allowed to stand for at least 2 minutes after the cycle ends
column18: before taking it out of the microwave and remember not to open the lid right away. The microwave sterilizer is easy to use and requires no rinsing and leaves no aftertaste or smell in the baby bottles. The durable
column19:
environment friendly and safe Microwave Sterilizer from Nuby keeps your baby boy\u2019s or baby girl\u2019s bottles sterile and makes life simpler.

\n
\n ']

'desc': [u'

Nuby Bath Tub (Yellow) Price: Rs.450

Bathing your baby at home with no one’s help can be a bit of a task. Holding your infant’s wobbly body and giving her a proper bath is not that easy. The Nuby Bath Tub is a perfect accessory that allows you to single handedly bathe your little angel in your own bath tub. This specially designed Bath Tub from Nuby has a contour that gives proper support to your tiny tot’s body and helps you in bathing the child effortlessly.

The durable plastic with which the Nuby Contour Bath Tub is made can be cleaned easily. The suction cups at the base of the Bath Tub offers a reliable grip to the Nuby tub and helps in keeping it in place when your baby is seated in it. With this Nuby Tub you can make sure that your bundle of joy gets the safest bath experience with you
